title: Error in Own Reporting
text: As a data producer, you have the responsibility to versee the data quality rules on your own report.

title: Remediation Prior to Report
text: As the data consumer, you are not responsible for remediating issues surrounding the data source because you are not the producer of the data in the source.

title: Quality of Fields Produced
text: The data quality team monitors data quality dashboards to hold parties accountable for remediating data quality issues.
